ack Activities:** Throughout 2024, 2025, and early 2026, SpaceX and xAI actively repurchased common and redeemable convertible preferred stock from eligible employees and existing shareholders at fair market value. Notably, $2.4 billion was repurchased from xAI employees as part of the merger consideration. All repurchased shares have been retired.\n\n### **6. Underwriter Relationships**\n*   **Conflicts of Interest:** The underwriters (including Morgan Stanley, Goldman Sachs, BofA, Citigroup, and J.P. Morgan) have extensive existing financial relationships with SpaceX. They serve as lenders/administrative agents under the SpaceX Bridge Loan and Credit Facility, and Morgan Stanley specifically advised SpaceX on the xAI acquisition.',
